definition: car/vehicle/CL:輛|辆[liang4]/machine/to shape with a lathe/Kangxi radical 159

sentences.english: We're going to take the morning train to Nanjing.
sentences.chinese: 我們打算坐早車去南京。

sentences.english: Getting up late means missing the early bus.
sentences.chinese: 起牀晚了意味着趕不上早車。

sentences.english: They got up early to catch the early bus.
sentences.chinese: 他們起牀早是爲了趕上早車。
